org.eclipse.papyrus.MARTE.MARTE_AnalysisModel.GQAM

Interface GaStep

  • All Superinterfaces:
    org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, GaScenario, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier, ResourceUsage, TimedElement, TimedProcessing
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    GaAcqStep, GaCommStep, GaRelStep, GaRequestedService, PaCommStep, PaRequestedStep, PaResPassStep, PaStep, SaCommStep, SaStep
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    GaAcqStepImpl, GaCommStepImpl, GaRelStepImpl, GaRequestedServiceImpl, GaStepImpl, PaCommStepImpl, PaRequestedStepImpl, PaResPassStepImpl, PaStepImpl, SaCommStepImpl, SaStepImpl

    public interface GaStep
extends GaScenario
    A representation of the model object 'Ga Step'.

    The following features are supported:

    • Is Atomic
    • Block T
    • Rep
    • Prob
    • Priority
    • Concur Res
    • Host
    • Serv Demand
    • Serv Count
    • Self Delay
    • Scenario
    • Child Scenario

    See Also:
    GQAMPackage.getGaStep()
